311
00:33:04.430 --> 00:33:06.350
<i>Kilencedik sugárút.</i>

312
00:33:13.940 --> 00:33:16.310
<i>Az ajtók záródnak.</i>

313
00:33:52.730 --> 00:33:55.270
A francba!

314
00:36:48.780 --> 00:36:53.360
